rd is subject to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{chapter 161F}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{chapters 357 through 358}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{chapter 468, subchapters I through III}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{chapter 468, subchapter IV, parts 1 and 2}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, or }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{chapter 468, subchapter V}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, as applicable, in acting relative to a special district authorized under any of those chapters.}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{b.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{However, the board may assume and exercise the powers and duties of a governing body under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{chapter 357}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{357A}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{357B}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{358}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, or }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{chapter 468, subchapter III}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, if a governing body established under one of those chapters has insufficient membership to perform its powers and duties, and the board, upon petition of the number of property owners within a proposed district and filing of a bond as provided in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 357A.2}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, may establish a service district within the unincorporated area of the county and exercise within the district the powers and duties granted in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{chapters 357}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{357A}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{357B}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{357C}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{357I}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{358}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{359}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{chapter 384, subchapter IV}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, or }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{chapter 468, subchapter III}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{8.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The power to establish and administer an air pollution control program in lieu of state administration is subject to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{sections 455B.144}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ and }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{455B.145}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{9.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The board shall issue permits, conduct inspections, and adopt standards related to the construction of semipublic sewage disposal systems, as defined in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 455B.171}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, in relation to authority delegated by the department of natural resources pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{sections 455B.174}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ and }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{455B.183}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{. Construction standards adopted pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this subsection}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ shall be consistent with and equivalent to the construction standards adopted by the environmental protection commission pursuant to }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 455B.173, subsection 3}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{. The county may adopt such standards by reference.}}}\par}{}{}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{1.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{a \u8211\'3f f.}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{[}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{S81, \'a7331.382(1)}}}{; }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{81 Acts, ch 117, \'a7381}}}{]}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{g.}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{[C51, \'a7828; R60, \'a71396; C73, \'a71372; C97, \'a72241; SS15, \'a72241; C24, 27, 31, 35, \'a753